<br>
EVER.<br>
<br>
Why?<br>
<br>
Cause it's 99.999997% of the time PERMA-CAMPED by a line of monks and monk twinks. I almost NEVER see another class there who isn't either with a monk or twinking a monk.<br>
<br>
Raster is a VERY rare spawn.<br>
<br>
VERY RARE.<br>
<br>
I've only heard of ONE MQ of the idol among my group of friends, guildmates and allies. Just one MQ.<br>
<br>
So go ... auction all you want for it people. It'll be a long, LONG while before you see it for sale.<br>
<br>
In other words ... it'll be a 40+ hour camp no matter what you do ... whether you camp Raster in Lower Guk OR you camp him in the bazaar.<br>
<br>
Enjoy your bottleneck.<br>
<br>
